OUT! LBW! Sri Lanka have the breakthrough but is it too late now! Time will tell!  Prabath Jayasuriya has been superb from the start of the day and his effort has paid off. He serves a full ball, angling around middle and off. The ball stays low off the deck and straightens a bit. Mohammad Rizwan presses forward to defend but gets beaten on the inside edge and gets pinged on the pads. A massive appeal for LBW and up goes the finger. That looked plumb as Rizwan has been given LBW but he refers it upstairs. Ultra Edge shows no bat. Ball Tracking shows three reds and Mohammad Rizwan has to walk back. Pakistan still need 66 runs to reach the target.
Howout: lbw b Prabath Jayasuriya

Commentary: Tossed up, on off, the arm ball. Salman prods to defend to silly point.
Tight from Jayasuriya! Fuller and on middle. Salman defends on the front foot.

This one spins around off, angling in and turns away sharply. Salman is tempted to defend on the front foot but gets beaten on the outside edge. The keeper removes the bails but the batter's back foot was grounded.
Slants it on middle, Salman gets off the mark as he sweeps it to fine leg.
Slower, flighted and around off. Shafique prods and gets a straight bat down to defend.
FOUR! More runs! Flatter and around off. Slaman reverse hits it to the vacant deep backward point. Prabath Jayasuriya runs from deep point but fails to stop it. Four runs.
Shorter and outside off. Salman punches it to point for one
Length and spinning around middle. Shafique tucks it to short leg who blocks it with his right hand.
Darted on the pads. Shafique nudges it past short leg and leg slip for a single.
Tossed up on middle. Salman leans and defends it out.

Too full and on off, pushed to covers. The bowler runs across and stops it. A quick single. While Prabath Jayasuriya is keeping things tight and creating pressure. Sri Lanka have failed to do the same from the other side.
Prabath Jayasuriya serves this full and going down leg, Agha Salman sweeps this wide of fine leg for a single.
Prabath Jayasuriya flights this full and in line with the stumps, Abdullah Shafique knocks this towards short mid off.
Flighted full outside off, Abdullah Shafique hits this straight to cover.
Tosses this one full on off, Abdullah Shafique fends this back towards the bowler.
This is a fraction short and on middle, Abdullah Shafique clips this through square leg for a single.
Prabath Jayasuriya serves this full on off, Agha Salman gets a stride forward and defends the ball back towards the bowler.
Ramesh Mendis begins with a slightly short delivery in line with the stumps, Abdullah Shafique stands tall and guides it towards mid-wicket.
Full and turning down leg side, Abdullah Shafique looks to flick this and misses.
This one is full as well on middle and leg, Abdullah Shafique clips this towards deep square leg for a single.
Ramesh Mendis goes short once again and outside off, Agha Salman goes back in the crease and fends it down into the pitch.

Ramesh Mendis flights this full on off, Agha Salman goes for the reverse sweep and plays under the ball. It hits his forearm and shoots up towards leg gully, There is an appeal but the umpire remains unmoved.
Ramesh Mendis serves this short once again and spinning down leg, Agha Salman misses his flick down leg.
Prabath Jayasuriya flights this full outside off, Abdullah Shafique knocks this to deep cover for a single.
This one is full on middle and leg, Agha Salman gets his front foot out of the way and hits it to the mid off fielder.
Goes full outside off, Agha Salman knocks this to the right of short cover.
Prabath Jayasuriya serves a really full delivery outside off, Agha Salman gets his bat down and digs the ball to the off side.
Once again full outside off, Agha Salman strokes this straight to short cover.
A fraction short on middle and leg, Agha Salman stands tall and defends down the pitch.
Ramesh Mendis goes full outside off, Abdullah Shafique gets his front foot forward and defends the ball to the cover region.
Ramesh Mendis is short again and in line with the stumps. Abdullah Shafique goes on one knee and pulls this to deep backward square leg for a single.
Agha Salman shimmies down the wicket and defends the ball on the full in line with the stumps.
This one is full outside off, Agha Salman pushes at it and gets an inside edge to square leg for a single.
Ramesh Mendis is a fraction short and gets the ball to spin down leg, Abdullah Shafique leaves this one alone.
This is full and turning into the pads, Abdullah Shafique clips this towards leg gully.
Prabath Jayasuriya serves this full on middle and leg, Agha Salman taps this to the right of the bowler.
This one is full outside off, Agha Salman goes to defend and gets an inside edge to square leg.
Goes full outside leg and gets the ball to spin away. Agha Salman looks to defend and gets the outside edge this time past the vacant gully region for a single.
Beaten! Prabath Jayasuriya serves this full outside off, Abdullah Shafique looks to defend and beats him with turn and bounce.
This one is full as well on a off stump line. Abdullah Shafique gets forward in defense.
Prabath Jayasuriya continues bowling full outside off, Abdullah Shafique covers the line of the ball and fends it back to the bowler.
Tossed up on middle. Salman prods and blocks it on the leg side.
Fuller again, around off. Salman gets forward and looks to sweep but it hits his left bicep and lobs to short leg who dives forward and takes it. An optimistic appeal follows but nothing happens.

A run out appeal but Salman is not out! Flatter and outside off. Salman taps it to backward point. Salman wants a single but is sent back. The fielder there hits at the stumps and appeals but the replay shows the batter was well in.
Angling down the leg side, kept out.
Fuller ball, outside off, driven to covers for a single.
Flatter and on middle, slightly slower. Shafique hangs back to block it out.
Too full and angling on off, Salman drives it to extra cover for a single.
Tossed up, slower and outside off, driven to point for an easy single.
Too full and on middle. Salman tries to play on the leg side, against the turn but mistimes it back to the bowler.
On middle. Blocked out.
Tossed up, on off, Agha pushes it to mid off.
An arm ball, fuller and around off. Salman prods and defends it out.
On the pads, flicked to the left of leg slip, all along the ground.
Slants on middle. Shafique nudges it to mid-wicket.

Was that a chance! This is too full and on middle. Shafique pre-meditates as he comes down the track and tries to loft over the bowler but didn't time well. Dhananjaya de Silva leaps and gets his hands to it but fails to stick it. Well, a chance goes begging. Two runs.
Angling on the pads, tucked to mid-wicket.
Around off and middle. Shafique keeps it out.
Too full, flighted and on middle. Shafique whips it through mid-wicket for a single.
Change of angle for Jayasuriya as he serves a full ball from over the wicket and down the leg side. Shafique tickles it to deep square leg for a single.
Too full and on middle. Salman blocks it out confidently.

OUT! CAUGHT BEHIND! Sri Lanka are still in the game! Jayasuriya serves a full ball from over the wicket and makes it to spin away from around off. Salman takes a big stride forward and tries to defend but fails to read the spin and gets an outside edge to the keeper, Niroshan Dickwella who takes it high to his right. Sri Lanka were convinced it was out. An appeal for caught behind and the finger goes up. Agha Salman takes the review. Ultra Edge shows a spike and Sri Lanka strike at the stroke of Lunch!
Howout: c Niroshan Dickwella b Prabath Jayasuriya

Commentary: Shorter and outside off. Ali punches it to cover.
Tossed up, sliding around off. Ali sweeps it to deep mid-wicket for a single.
Beauty! Fuller ball from over the wicket and landing on middle, it spins sharply across the batter. Shafique looks to defend but gets a thick outside edge and lands safely away from first slip.

FOUR! Ali will always play aggressive cricket! A loopy ball, around off, turning in. Ali skips down and heaves it, not of the middle but over the mid-wicket fielder and in the gap for a boundary. 300 up for Pakistan.

OUT! TAKEN! Another one bites the dust! Sri Lanka are still hanging there! de Silva serves a length ball, around middle and spins down the leg side. Ali hangs on the back foot and gets low to slog-sweep it over deep square leg. The intent was right but not the execution as he fails to get enough distance and Maheesh Theekshana holds onto it. Pakistan need 39 more runs to win. Sri Lanka need 4 wickets.
Howout: c Maheesh Theekshana b Dhananjaya de Silva

Commentary: On the pads, tucked to square leg for a single.
Flighted, full and on middle. Nawaz blocks it out.
Tossed up on off, turning away. Nawaz prods to defend but gets a thick outside edge to point.
Flatter and outside off, stays low. It is hit to covers.
Prabath Jayasuriya tosses this full and well outside leg. Abdullah Shafique plays the turn and defends well.
Prabath Jayasuriya serves this full outside leg and gets it to pitch on the rough. Turns sharply and hits the back leg. An appeal follows but it is missing off pole clearly.
Full delivery on leg, Abdullah Shafique fends this back to the bowler.
Full and in line with the stumps. Defends it to the cover region.
Turns sharply and beats the outside edge. Prabath Jayasuriya serves this full one leg, Abdullah Shafique goes to fend on the back foot and gets squared up.
Full delivery sliding down leg, Abdullah Shafique looks to sweep and misses.
Dhananjaya de Silva serves this full outside off, Mohammad Nawaz fends this solidly back to the right of the bowler.
Goes really full outside off, Mohammad Nawaz looks to sweep and plays over the ball. Goes through to the keeper.
Dhananjaya de Silva goes full outside off once again, Mohammad Nawaz dabs this down toward silly point.
Serves this one short outside off, Mohammad Nawaz uses the crease and goes back to punch this to deep cover for a single.
Full delivery pitching outside leg and turning firther away to the leg side. Abdullah Shafique looks to play and then leaves it alone.
Dhananjaya de Silva goes full on the pads, Abdullah Shafique clips this to backward square leg.
Sharp turn from the rough. Prabath Jayasuriya pulls his length back a bit outside off, Mohammad Nawaz tries to defend on the front foot. The ball hits his chest.
This one is fired full onto the pads, Mohammad Nawaz clips this to mid-wicket.
Prabath Jayasuriya serves this full outside off, Mohammad Nawaz wants to get his front foot outside off to defend. Gets an inside edge onto his body.
This is full outside off, Mohammad Nawaz fends this towards short cover.
Prabath Jayasuriya goes full once again and gets the ball to turn into the pads as Mohammad Nawaz looks to defend. Hits the pads and lobs up towards short leg.

Huge appeal from Prabath Jayasuriya! Serves this full outside off, Mohammad Nawaz pushes forward and hits the pad, and goes to short leg. Sri Lanka do not have a review but this goes clearly off the pad.
Full and on the pads, Abdullah Shafique gets down the wicket and clips it over mid-wicket for a couple of runs.
Tossed up on middle, solidly defended on the front foot.
Full and in line with the stumps, Abdullah Shafique fends this to the right of the bowler.
This one is full and on middle, Abdullah Shafique goes back in the crease and knocks it back to the bowler.
Full delivery on the pads, clipped towards mid-wicket for a brace.
Beaten! Dhananjaya de Silva flights this full outside off, Abdullah Shafique looks to play for the spin and gets beaten by the straight delivery.
Prabath Jayasuriya goes full and wide outside off, Mohammad Nawaz works this wide of mid off and gets off strike.
This is full and going down leg, Abdullah Shafique looks to flick this and misses.
Goes full once again and pitches this outside leg, Abdullah Shafique taps this to short mid-wicket.
Full delivery on the pads, Abdullah Shafique clips this towards square leg with soft hands and rushes between the wickets for a couple of runs.
This is full on middle and off, Abdullah Shafique fends this and gets and an outside edge towards point.
This is full on middle and leg, Abdullah Shafique guides this through point to take a single and retain strike.
Darted on the pads, staying low. Shafique dead bats it.
Gives more flight to this one and bowls it on the pads, it is flicked to square leg for a single.
Leg bye! Angles a full ball on the pads. Nawaz defends the wrong line and gets hit on the pads. It rolls to square leg for a leg bye.
Shorter and around leg. Kept out.
Again on the pads. Shafique plays with soft hands to short leg.
Shafique will keep the strike! Pakistan are inching closer! This is full and on the pads, it is swept behind square on the leg side for one. Shafique moves to 149 now.
Tossed up, angling across the batter. Blocked out on the front foot.
150 up for Shafique! He raises his bat but he knows this milestone will not matter much without the victory! Shorter and outside off. Shafique slaps it to deep ppoint for a single.

Superb fielding! Full and on middle. Nawaz sweeps it hard and to deep square leg. Ramesh Mendis to his right, and dives to make a superb stop and save a couple of runs. Nawaz was struggling for the second but made it. Sri Lanka fighting for every single run.

Three runs! Mohammad Nawaz looking like he wants to get home in a hurry. Prabath Jayasuriya serves this full on the rough, Mohammad Nawaz gets a stride forward to the pitch of the delivery and strokes it through covers for three runs.
Tossed up on middle. Shafique leans and blocks it.
Flighted, full and on leg. Shafique bunts it to square leg for a single. 7 runs off the over. Good one for Pakistan! They need 19 more runs for the victory.
On the pads, flicked to short leg.
Similar delivery! On the pads. Shafique defends it out.
Fuller and down the leg side. Shafique sweeps it but leg slip gets his hand to it.
Around middle and leg. Kept out.

DROPPED! Has Kasun Rajitha dropped the game? What a chance this is! Abdullah Shafique pre-meditates as he comes down the track and tries to slog this full ball towards deep square leg. There was not much pace on the ball so Abdullah Shafique had to generate the power. It goes really high towards deep square leg where Kasun Rajitha runs forward and has all the time in the world to get into position. Goes right through his hands as he fails to hold on it. Ohh, boy! What a massive chance!
On middle, swept to deep square leg for one.
Full and on middle. Nawaz defends on the front foot.
A loopy ball on middle. Nawaz drills it to long on for a single.
On a length and on middle. Shafique lunges to block it.
Fuller and on middle. Shafique pushes it gently to long off for one more.
Too full and outside off. Nawaz punches it to covers for a single.
Toosed up, down the leg side. Shafique tickles it to backward square leg, straight to the fielder and calls for a single but changes his decision quickly and gets back into the crease.
Tossed up, outside off. Nawaz square drives it to point for a single.
Way down the leg side. Shafique helps it past short leg and leg slip for one more.
Shorter and down the leg side, gripping in the surface. Nawaz opens his body and tries to flick but misses and gets hit on the pads.
Flatter and outside off. Nawaz cuts it to deep point for a single.
Slower, flatter and down the leg side. Shafique flicks it to short leg.
Again this is down the leg side. Shafique plays with soft hands and to square leg.
Pakistan need 10 runs now! On middle, flicked to deep mid-wicket for a single.
Tossed up, full and on middle. Abdullah Shafique looks to defend but outer edges it past first slip and to third man for a single.
Fuller and on middle, pushed back to the bowler.
Slower through the air and on middle. Nawaz defends it out.
Tries to angle across a full ball, around off. Nawaz pads it away.
A single as Nawaz steers this length ball to point.
This is a fraction short in line with the stumps, Mohammad Nawaz clips this towards square leg for a single.
Goes full outside off, Abdullah Shafique taps this towards point and takes a run. Just 6 runs are needed now and Sri Lanka giving away some easy singles
Flighted full outside off, Mohammad Nawaz fends this to the left of the bowler.
Full once again outside off, Mohammad Nawaz knocks this into the cover region.
FOUR! Pakistan are nearly there! Fatter and around leg. Nawaz sweeps it very gently but the outfield helps the ball to race away to the fine leg fence.
Shorter and down the leg side, spinning into the batter. Nawaz tries to finish off the match with a big wild sweep but misses.
Tossed up on off, spinning away. Abdullah Shafique looks to sweep but misses.

FOUR! Abdullah Shafique hits the winning runs! A brilliant match winning knock from the young man! Shorter and outside off. Abdullah Shafique gets on the back foot and slaps it to covers for a boundary. Pakistan win by 4 wickets and go 1-0 up in the series.
